9397405685914188.Text: I gave Han-Ammu the Robe of Erur-Dan the Wise and made a little speech about wisdom and symbols and responsibility. I believe he has taken the lesson to heart, and will consider accepting his responsibilities as ashkhan, and consider naming me Nerevarine. But he said he does not need the robe, and he asked me to keep it.
